line_1: Till with a joyless smile the eye beholds
line_2: Say, shall the terrors thy pale flag unfolds,

line_1: In which she oft herself beholds.
line_2: Her left a magic mirror holds,

line_1: The germ of future Worlds beholds,
line_2: The secrets of dark space unfolds;

line_1: And in herself MY Muse beholds.
line_2: Before the glass her charms unfolds,

line_1: The humbler Shepherd here with joy beholds
line_2: The approv'd economy of crowded folds,
